<br>
I'm theoretically supposed to run a Nagafen raid later today...<br>
I don't know if I have the emotional strength to do that at this point.  A part of my brain is still waiting/hoping that I'll wake up and that the New York skyline will have remained as I have remembered it for the past 27 years...<br>
<br>
There's a thread running on KGC considering suspending all large target requirements for a day or more.  If the requirements are not lifted, I will do my best to run a successful Nagafen raid... but I think we'd all prefer to have a little time to reflect on todays events.<br>
<br>
I've heard from some of my friends and family that live in the Washington DC and New York areas... but I've a few reletives living in New York that no one has heard from as of yet.  Long distance phone lines are clogged beyond belief and I doubt we'll have word from them for a day or two...<br>
<br>
My thoughts and prayers go out to all of you in similar circumstances. <p>-Kommisar Nils "Can-Head" Hansen -- Guild Officer. Master Smith. Tank.
